io.discloader.discloader.common.event

Interface IEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventListenerAdapter

    public interface IEventListener
    Interface for DiscLoader events

    How To Use

     DiscLoader loader = new DiscLoader();
 
 loader.addListener(new EventListenerAdapter() {
 
        @Override
        public void Ready(DiscLoader loader) {
                // do something
        }
 
 });
    Since:
    0.0.3
    Author:
    Perry Berman

        During the PreInit phase of startup, after all mods have been discovered, The ModRegistry executes this event on the mod the registry is attempting to load. All commands must be registered on this event being called in your mod.
